## ðŸŽ¯ Project Overview

This repository demonstrates a full end-to-end **Cybersecurity Awareness & Social Engineering Resilience Program** â€” from survey and needs assessment through program design, training rollout, and performance reporting.

The project was designed to simulate how a cybersecurity analyst develops and manages an **enterprise-wide awareness initiative**, tailored especially for organizations in **Operational Technology (OT) and SCADA environments**.

> ðŸ§© *Goal:* Build a measurable, data-driven awareness culture that reduces phishing risk, strengthens security behavior, and supports compliance with NIST SP 800-50 and ISO 27001 controls.

---

## ðŸ§  Objectives

- Assess organizational awareness maturity through baseline surveys  
- Develop policies, communication plans, and stakeholder engagement materials  
- Conduct targeted phishing simulations and hands-on awareness training  
- Measure success using key performance indicators (KPIs) and dashboards  
- Continuously improve program design through quarterly review cycles  

