## ðŸ§© Framework Alignment

This program aligns with major cybersecurity frameworks:

- **NIST SP 800-50** â€” Building an Information Technology Security Awareness and Training Program  
- **NIST SP 800-53 (AT-1, AT-2, AT-3)** â€” Awareness and Training Controls  
- **ISO/IEC 27001 A.7.2.2** â€” Information Security Awareness, Education, and Training  
- **CIS Control 14** â€” Security Awareness and Skills Training  

